main event: An unidentified object resembling an aircraft was observed over a body of water on GCA radar at Goose AFB.
interesting points: The object was traveling at approximately 25 miles per hour and had an altitude of less than 4000 feet due to radar limitations., All aircraft in the area were accounted for., The object exhibited a clear, steady radar track but was not visually confirmed., The incident involved a radar signal that resembled an aircraft with no visual evidence., Weather conditions included scattered clouds at 4,500 feet during the observation.
